_sText:
Bringing back the Jump maps.

Jump your way to the end of the map, if you fall you will be teleported to the nearest checkpoint.
At the end, someone will need to stand on a button which opens the door to let other people in, which means someone must stay behind.


3 large jump rooms and final/credits room where knives are located to pick up.
A song plays when someone enters the winner room, there you can teleport to checkpoints to play over again.


Have fun with my favorite map type, the old Jump maps!
